videos.description: De'Andre Hunter makes the extra pass to Kyle Guy for a 3-pointer, then Guy pulls up for another long ball on the next possession.
videos.headline: Guy brings crowd alive with back-to-back 3s

videos.description: Ty Jerome comes off the screen and dumps it off to Mamadi Diakite, who powers up for the strong two-handed finish.
videos.headline: Jerome finds Diakite for rim-rocking slam
